<section id="Tagging_Security_Groups" remap="TID_22647">
	<title>Tagging Security Groups</title>
	<para>
		Apply tags to security groups to categorize them. Before assigning tags, create them using instructions in the <emphasis>CloudForms Management Engine Settings and Operations Guide</emphasis>.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Tag Security Groups</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to menu:Clouds[Security Groups].
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select the security group to tag.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1941.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Policy)</guibutton>, and then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2158.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Edit Tags)</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select a customer tag to assign from the dropdown menu.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select a value to assign.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>Save</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>